metadata.name: Etherminati Skateboards #5699
metadata.description:
Introducing Etherminati Skateboards, the inaugural NFT in an exciting series that offers tangible value. This unique collection merges digital art and physical merchandise, providing collectors with multiple redemption options.

With captivating digital artwork, Etherminati Skateboards goes beyond aesthetics. Collectors can redeem their NFT for a high-quality skateboard (additional cost), or simply burn the NFT during the redemption event to unlock an exclusive Profile Picture (PFP).

Join the Etherminati community today and experience the true value of this collectionâ€”a seamless blend of digital and physical worlds, extending ownership beyond the digital realm.

More details about this project and redemption information will be available on etherminati.com as soon as they are available.
